Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:05.94,Italics,news,0000,0000,0000,,The salinity in the Narunami area around \Nnoon is expected to be 57 per mill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:09.39,Italics,new,0000,0000,0000,,Around 6PM, it will rise to 60 per mill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:11.73,Italics,news,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the saltflake snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:13.63,Italics,news,0000,0000,0000,,the water temperature \Nis expected to drop,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.63,0:00:16.95,Italics,news,0000,0000,0000,,and the temperature of Shioshishio \Nis expected to drop to 15 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:19.30,Italics,news,0000,0000,0000,,Next is the weather on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:21.50,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It actually falls on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.97,0:00:22.25,Italics,news,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The Shioshishio Peninsula \Nwill continue to be sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:23.54,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,The saltflake snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:26.16,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.16,0:00:30.02,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It was different, even a bit creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:34.13,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if everyone in Shishio \Nknows it fell on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:36.00,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as they find out,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:39.32,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,they'll say it's Ooshi's fault because \Nthey refused to do the Ofunehiki
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:43.30,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,and the Sea God is meting\Nout divine punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.01,0:00:45.37,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:48.95,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing how Dad and the \Nothers are, I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:50.91,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:55.06,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that Dad is worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.06,0:00:55.98,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's not—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:00:58.99,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari, I think you should \Ngo home after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:01.13,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:02.82,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:05.16,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I got a whole bunch \Nof snow and made this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:08.38,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:09.84,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,A fish cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:11.62,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's a snow sea slug!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.28,0:01:13.88,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know what it was, Aka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:16.59,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.03,0:01:18.89,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:21.43,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,It's even better if you add these.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.37,0:01:26.37,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it'll last till Daddy gets home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:27.94,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It won't melt that fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:30.56,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:32.61,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Daddy will \Nknow what it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:33.73,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he will.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:35.07,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Look how cute it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:43.04,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that saltflake snow \Nfell on the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:47.50,Main,guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,So it's going to keep getting \Ncolder the way the prophecy said?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:51.49,Main,guy 3,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't forgotten about the Sea God.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:56.64,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,But haven't you noticed that the sacred \Nfire's going out faster lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:01:58.37,Main,guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:03.80,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:05.45,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find out the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.45,0:02:07.64,Main,guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:08.57,Main,guy 3,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:10.31,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,You're so noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:12.24,Main,guy 4,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uroko-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:16.07,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Come now. Hurry and take your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:21.39,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Uroko-sama, if you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:24.54,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,There is only one reason I have \Nasked you all to gather here today...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:30.43,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to talk to you about \Nthe calamity that approaches us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:04.01,Episode-Title,title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Nine:\NUnknown Warmth
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:10.43,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the snow \Ndidn't fall for very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:11.28,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:14.25,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the Sea God is mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:16.31,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:22.19,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:30.73,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Dad better not be drinking a lot and \Nskipping meals just because I'm not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:33.33,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, what's he doing about food?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:35.71,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:37.71,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.96,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Mornin'. Whatcha doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:43.08,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I was trying to figure out where to fix it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:46.82,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing here so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:50.19,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we were sort of thrown out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:52.68,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,We were told that adults had \Nan important meeting to go to,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:55.49,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,so we should head to school early.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:57.22,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What's that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.22,0:05:01.35,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it has to do with the \Nsaltflake snow falling on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:04.00,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Adults are always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:07.22,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,They think it's okay to keep \Neverything a secret from kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:09.70,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Ojoshi-sama's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.86,0:05:14.09,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be doing the Ofunehiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:29.53,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,We really want to do this to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:30.93,Let's do the Ofunehiki,board,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do the Ofunehiki
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:30.93,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,With just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:33.64,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we might as well finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:37.10,Main,shimizu,0000,0000,0000,,And we feel bad for Ojoshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:40.76,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask my Gramps for a boat to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:42.38,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,There you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:44.39,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,We can do this, right, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:46.62,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:48.14,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:50.83,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all make sure it's \Na success no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:53.55,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Once we're done, I'll definitely \Ntreat you guys to ramen this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.48,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps said we could use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:02.60,Main,aki,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:04.57,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,But it's smaller than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:06.17,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Let's repaint it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:08.76,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,We should probably reinforce it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.88,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:13.60,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:17.36,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.99,0:06:20.13,Main,isamu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:22.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're putting too much into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:23.52,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:26.60,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:28.32,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna get hurt like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:30.05,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:35.91,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's more like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:40.94,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,I think we're all getting hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:41.58,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:44.13,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go make us something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:46.58,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get some things from Saya Mart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:49.66,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You better not be doing this\Njust so you can have a snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:51.01,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:54.43,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:57.31,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're just gonna get fat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:58.82,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari's trying really hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.32,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:00.56,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:02.33,Main,shimi,0000,0000,0000,,It's heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:04.04,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:05.48,Main,shimi,0000,0000,0000,,You're a lifesaver!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.74,0:07:08.65,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You guys came!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:09.84,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:13.37,Main,ega,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:16.19,Main,ega,0000,0000,0000,,This is my awesome creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:18.02,Main,ega,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:20.16,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,That's the hip microwave! \NLeave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:25.13,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Why are there shumai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:29.89,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what'd be good...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.05,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Manaka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:34.89,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Akari-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:40.10,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Something that'll keep you \Nwarm is probably best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:42.88,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,This summer's a bit chilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:45.83,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Something warm and from the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:48.07,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, has Hikari said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:49.13,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:52.34,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Like about the sea or home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:58.01,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Hikari's \Nnot worried about Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:08:00.00,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.75,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun really is worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:06.75,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun's worried about your dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:10.51,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:15.16,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,They both care about each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:17.55,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,but this isn't going well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.29,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:35.14,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:48.08,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, could I use your—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:47.46,Always Smiling,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Always Smiling\NSaya Mart
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:53.17,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Um, this is, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:55.46,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:59.43,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu also did that quite a \Nbit when he first came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.72,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,"When he first came here"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:05.61,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu-kun wasn't born in this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:08.24,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,He came here on his \Nown when he was nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:09.22,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:11.24,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he come by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:14.45,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,His parents live in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:18.24,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu-kun came by himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:22.12,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,So Tsumugu-kun has always been \NTsumugu-kun since he was little...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:24.76,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:26.91,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought that \NTsumugu-kun is really good
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.91,0:09:30.79,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,at finding himself and \Nthings that are around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:34.59,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he found his love for \Nthe sea when he was young, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:38.21,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's why he \Nchose to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:41.00,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,His precious...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:43.97,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Because he knows what's precious to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:09:58.69,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:06.16,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:18.13,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know? Apparently Café \NTriangle is the place for meets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:19.51,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Meats?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:21.02,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,You mince meat there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:21.94,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:25.00,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,It's a place where guys and girls \Nare friendly with each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:28.14,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like your mouth's \Nworking just fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.65,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,but how about your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:31.78,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're working!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:33.69,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:37.30,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do more and—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:38.20,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:41.74,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna head back to \Nschool and get some tools,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:43.78,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,so could you see if there's\N wood in the back for reinforcing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:45.26,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:48.75,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm counting \Non you little ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:10:59.41,Main,chisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to help you paint?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:09.56,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Your Ena probably dried up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:14.90,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:15.98,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:18.49,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,We painted it really nice! How's tha—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:19.62,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Chisaki? Did she go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:22.72,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:23.81,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:44.59,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:49.19,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay now, don't worry. \NSo you can head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:52.27,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still need a sea slug?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:56.47,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.28,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need one anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:04.28,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you're \Ngiving up on Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:05.40,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:07.38,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,"Why?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:12.52,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have to change... so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:16.04,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what "change" means to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:20.46,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, that's what it means \Nto become an adult, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:22.57,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just keep thinking about yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:24.58,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,and you have to keep moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:26.78,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you're \Nneglecting your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:27.51,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:30.35,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Because you can't forgive \Nhow you are right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:33.57,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu-kun, you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:36.15,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:39.65,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't dislike how you are right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:44.55,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:49.53,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki! Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:53.37,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not feeling well, so I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:56.52,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:03.22,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I really hate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.44,0:13:08.75,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,So he makes you make \Nexpressions like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:10.13,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.35,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,The village...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:20.36,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,is different from usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:30.03,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:40.04,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you need this anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:47.91,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:51.87,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! It took me a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:53.24,Main,girls,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:54.44,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:55.80,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,We're already done for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:58.40,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where'd Chisaki and Kaname go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:01.12,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,They went home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:04.21,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they had something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:08.98,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Looks like the food's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:13.41,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That's the shumai for \Nthe inside of the microwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:15.43,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:16.90,Main,aki,0000,0000,0000,,Nice catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:20.19,Main,ega,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Be careful with my shumai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:23.08,Main,ega,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how hard I \Nworked on that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:24.69,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:28.10,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It's seafood and pork soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:29.04,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:31.80,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Putting pork in seafood soup is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:31.47,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.79,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:38.96,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it'd be nice if things that were \Nraised in the sea and on the surface got along.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:43.11,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The sea and the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:52.42,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:55.20,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,That's for making my knees buckle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.21,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's totally different!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:15:00.12,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's different for a lot of reasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:02.71,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:07.45,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here right now because you \Nwere there for me, Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:08.64,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:10.92,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:12.81,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What are you being all serious fo—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:17.54,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,You feel reassured when \Nsomeone is with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:20.73,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,You taught me lots.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:24.03,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:26.23,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,So... And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:31.05,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,If it's hard for you to go \Nback home, I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:33.42,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:34.45,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:37.14,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I feel reassured when you're next to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:38.99,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm sure your dad feels the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:40.26,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,And I know you do, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:45.30,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,If you can tell each other you care\Nabout each other, you'll become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:47.42,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be happier!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.98,0:15:58.92,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:02.68,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:05.11,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, what the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:09.13,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I said that I'd support her...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:12.17,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think I can control myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:13.61,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Food's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:15.66,Main,all,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.25,Main,all,0000,0000,0000,,Looks great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:19.60,Main,all,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:36.75,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Mom? Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:40.23,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:42.31,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:45.06,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:48.52,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka, you can't go \Nto the surface anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:49.61,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:59.58,Sakishima,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Sakishima
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:02.08,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka's your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:06.58,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,She's your friend, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:09.92,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:13.40,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Now if you'll open your \Ntextbook to page 48—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:14.69,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:22.28,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't really sleep \Nwell last night, and so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:25.23,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:27.31,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,So at least you showed up, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:27.96,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:32.86,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Well, all of the Shioshishio \Nkids didn't show up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:34.49,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to contact them \Nbut couldn't reach them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:36.61,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:47.04,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Those adults are trying to \Nstop the Ofunehiki again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.06,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:53.55,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go back to the village and \Nsettle this once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:57.01,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:03.51,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna tell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:07.02,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna tell all the old guys \Nand Dad... All of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:37.99,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What... is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:07.05,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd everyone go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:09.05,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:12.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Did something \Nhappen to the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.11,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,So you've come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:15.09,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:18.55,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Let's hurry \Nand go see Uroko-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:21.68,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to go see Uroko-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:23.27,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Just come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:25.13,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:26.51,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I said let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:28.06,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:29.81,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:32.55,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.22,0:19:35.44,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I... Hii-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:38.50,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka, you were told \Nnot to leave your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:39.84,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:40.82,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:42.52,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:45.91,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:57.16,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Since I was gone, the \Nvillage totally seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:19:59.51,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,When I got home last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:05.77,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,there were a lot of adults waiting and \Nthey said not to go up to the surface again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:09.52,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,My dad wouldn't let me out of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:11.02,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go up to the surface?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.51,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.51,0:20:14.73,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what they \Nsaid when I got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:17.19,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But why? Why'd they say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:18.72,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:20.94,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,They said it was \Ndangerous on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:22.66,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,So they said that \NChii-chan and Kaname...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:25.21,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,that none of us could leave the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:27.87,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Then why'd you come outside by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:29.49,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.09,0:20:32.54,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Because I had to tell you, Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:39.50,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we care about each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:45.55,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka's feelings and my \Nfeelings are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.73,0:20:49.76,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:51.71,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I had to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:53.92,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The way I feel about Manaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:55.79,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Because I had to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:15.62,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.33,0:21:25.69,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.52,0:21:41.92,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.81,0:21:49.77,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:51.87,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:55.32,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen on the surface?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.42,0:23:32.45,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,The world becomes more and more gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.45,0:23:34.24,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,The humans will forget the Sea God...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.24,0:23:36.22,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,This is the story of \Nhumans themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.22,0:23:38.64,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,The humans will not be able to bear \Nthe cold that is about to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:40.06,Episode-Title - Copy,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Ten: The Saltflake \NSnow Falls and Falls
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:40.87,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,You need to make your choice.
